fts - full text search
======================

Summary
-------
Full text search for html files with tokyodystopia and snap web framework.

Commands overview
-----------------
For detailed argument, run `fts --help`.

* `fts index`
    * Index html files under given directory, and write indexed data.

* `fts serve`
    * Run server program with given template path and db path.

Database schema
---------------
* Database for searching text
  * id -> Body text

* Database for other data. $(ID) is integer number.
  * uri:$(ID) -> uri of the content
  * text:$(ID) -> body text of content
